UPSTREAM ATTRIBUTIONS

This project integrates concepts and patterns from the following upstream
repositories. Each is subject to its own license. See docs/licenses.md for
individual license details.

- agents.md (agentsmd/agents.md) — MIT
- skills (anthropics/skills) — MIT / Apache-2.0
- harness (revfactory/harness) — check upstream
- deer-flow (bytedance/deer-flow) — Apache-2.0
- AutoResearchClaw (aiming-lab/AutoResearchClaw) — check upstream
- supermemory (supermemoryai/supermemory) — Apache-2.0
- autoresearch (karpathy/autoresearch) — MIT
- awesome-claude-code-subagents (VoltAgent) — check upstream
- superpowers (obra/superpowers) — check upstream
- PaperBanana (dwzhu-pku/PaperBanana) — check upstream
- agency-agents (msitarzewski/agency-agents) — check upstream
- ClawTeam (HKUDS/ClawTeam) — check upstream

No upstream code is vendored unless explicitly noted in upstreams/manifest.yaml.
Integration is conceptual and structural, not source-code based.
